				FREDO
		Hiya, Freddie Corleone.

				MICHAEL
		Mio fratello.

Then Bussetta offers his hand back to Fredo.

				FREDO
			(taking off his jacket)
		What a trip, Jesus Christ, the
		whole time I'm thinking what if
